<template><div><h1 id="utilizare-avansata-a-props-urilor" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#utilizare-avansata-a-props-urilor"><span>Utilizare avansat캒 a props-urilor</span></a></h1>
<p>칉n lec탵ia anterioar캒, am discutat despre componente 칥n React 탳i abordarea bazat캒 pe componente pentru crearea interfe탵elor utilizatorilor. 칉n aceast캒 lec탵ie, vom explora props-urile (props) 탳i caracteristicile lor.</p>
<p>Props-urile sunt, 칥n esen탵캒, argumentele unei func탵ii care permit influen탵area rand캒rii elementelor 칥n interiorul componentelor 탳i logica func탵ion캒rii lor. Ca 탳i un argument, un prop poate fi orice: o func탵ie, un obiect, un array, un 탳ir de caractere, un num캒r.</p>
<p>탲ti탵i deja c캒 React, c칙nd lucreaz캒 cu componente, combin캒 atributele JSX 칥ntr-un singur obiect - <mark>props</mark>.</p>
<p>칉ntr-o component캒 de clas캒, accesul la acest obiect se poate ob탵ine prin <mark>this.props</mark>, iar 칥ntr-o component캒 func탵ional캒, <mark>props</mark> este disponibil ca primul argument al func탵iei:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">Heading</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>h1<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>text<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>h1<span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>

<span class="token keyword">const</span> root <span class="token operator">=</span> ReactDOM<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">createRoot</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>document<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">querySelector</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'#root'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
root<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">render</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>Heading text<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"Titlul unui articol interesant"</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Ca nume al argumentului, este obi탳nuit s캒 se foloseasc캒 <mark>props</mark>.
Recomand캒m s캒 numi탵i argumentul exact a탳a: acest lucru va simplifica percep탵ia codului dvs. de c캒tre al탵i dezvoltatori, deoarece mul탵i dintre ei urmeaz캒 탳i ei acest principiu.</p>
<p>칉n lec탵ia despre <a href="/base/composition">compozi탵ie 탳i extragerea componentelor</a>, a탵i v캒zut deja c캒 pot exista mai multe props-uri 탳i structura lor permite 칥ncorporarea:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Product</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>p<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>productData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>p<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* Costum de scafandru */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>productData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>price<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>span<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* 14299 */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">ShoppingCart</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>h1<span class="token operator">></span>Co탳 de cump캒r캒turi<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>h1<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>Product productData<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token literal-property property">name</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"Costum de scafandru"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token literal-property property">price</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">14299</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n acest exemplu, componenta <mark>ShoppingCart</mark> &quot;randeaz캒&quot; o alt캒 component캒 - <mark>Product</mark>.
Ca argumente (props-uri), i se transmite un obiect cu dou캒 valori: <mark>name</mark> 탳i <mark>price</mark>.</p>
<p>Pentru a face codul mai lizibil, ar trebui s캒 simplifica탵i structura props-urilor transmise componentei 탳i s캒 utiliza탵i ca argumente primitive. Acest lucru nu va afecta performan탵a, deoarece React este foarte rapid, dar lucrul cu primitivele este mai simplu.</p>
<p>Privi탵i exemplul 칥n care <mark>props</mark> este un obiect complex:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// Component캒</span>
<span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Product</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>p<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>productData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>p<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* Costum de scafandru */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>productData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>price<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>span<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* 14299 */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token comment">// Utilizarea componentei</span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>Product productData<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token literal-property property">name</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"Costum de scafandru"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token literal-property property">price</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">14299</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Codul care utilizeaz캒 aceast캒 component캒 pare complicat, iar implementarea intern캒 necesit캒 mai mult캒 aten탵ie din partea dezvoltatorului. S캒 simplific캒m aceast캒 component캒:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// Component캒</span>
<span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Product</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>p<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>p<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* Costum de scafandru */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>price<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>span<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token comment">/* 14299 */</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token comment">// Utilizarea componentei</span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>Product name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"Costum de scafandru"</span> price<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token number">14299</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Din exemplu se vede c캒 implementarea s-a simplificat, iar utilizarea componentei a devenit mai declarativ캒.</p>
<h2 id="props-urile-pot-fi-doar-citite" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#props-urile-pot-fi-doar-citite"><span>Props-urile pot fi doar citite</span></a></h2>
<p>Componentele React trebuie s캒 se comporte ca func탵ii &quot;pure&quot; 칥n raport cu props-urile lor, indiferent dac캒 sunt func탵ionale sau de clas캒. Acest lucru 칥nseamn캒 c캒 componentele nu ar trebui s캒 scrie ceva 칥n props-urile lor. S캒 analiz캒m acest lucru pe exemplul func탵iilor &quot;pure&quot; 탳i &quot;impure&quot;.</p>
<p>Func탵ia <mark>formatPrice</mark> este &quot;pur캒&quot;, deoarece</p>
<p>nu modific캒 datele de intrare 탳i returneaz캒 칥n mod previzibil acela탳i rezultat pentru acelea탳i argumente:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">formatPrice</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">price</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">return</span> price <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'MDL'</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n schimb, func탵ia <mark>notificationSettings</mark> este &quot;impur캒&quot;, deoarece scrie date 칥n propriul s캒u argument - obiectul <mark>user</mark>:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">notificationSettings</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">user<span class="token punctuation">,</span> notificationValue</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  user<span class="token punctuation">.</span>notifications <span class="token operator">=</span> notificationValue<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Pentru ca dezvoltarea 칥n React s캒 r캒m칙n캒 previzibil캒 탳i convenabil캒, props-urile trebuie s캒 fie accesibile doar pentru citire.</p>
<p>칉n lec탵iile urm캒toare, vom discuta cum s캒 influen탵캒m props-urile unei componente din interiorul acestei componente.</p>
<h2 id="expresii-javascript-ca-props-uri" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#expresii-javascript-ca-props-uri"><span>Expresii JavaScript ca props-uri</span></a></h2>
<p>Ca props-uri, pute탵i transmite orice expresii JavaScript.
Pentru acest lucru, trebuie s캒 le 칥nconjura탵i cu <mark>{}</mark>. De exemplu, 칥n acest JSX:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>MusicGenreItem genre<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">'rock'</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'&amp;'</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> <span class="token string">'roll'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n componenta <mark>MusicGenreItem</mark>, valoarea <mark>props.genre</mark> va fi egal캒 cu <mark>rock&amp;roll</mark>, deoarece expresia <mark>'rock' + '&amp;' + 'roll'</mark> va fi evaluat캒. Acela탳i lucru este valabil 탳i pentru func탵ii:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">sayHi</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">name</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token template-string"><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span><span class="token string">Salut, </span><span class="token interpolation"><span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">${</span>name<span class="token interpolation-punctuation punctuation">}</span></span><span class="token string">!</span><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span></span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>

<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>WelcomeComponent textToRender<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token function">sayHi</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">'Nicolai'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n acest exemplu, 칥n prop-ul <mark>textToRender</mark> va ajunge rezultatul execut캒rii func탵iei <mark>sayHi('Nicolai')</mark>, adic캒 탳irul <mark>&quot;Salut, Nicolai!&quot;</mark>.</p>
<p>Operatorii <mark>if</mark>, <mark>switch</mark> 탳i ciclul <mark>for</mark> nu sunt expresii 칥n JavaScript. Din acest motiv, nu pot fi aplicate direct 칥n JSX.
Pentru a le utiliza, trebuie mai 칥nt칙i s캒 ob탵ine탵i rezultatul lucr캒rii acestor operatori, iar apoi acest rezultat s캒-l plasa탵i 칥n codul JSX:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">TrafficLightComponent</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">let</span> action<span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token keyword">switch</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>color<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> 
        <span class="token keyword">case</span> <span class="token string">"red"</span><span class="token operator">:</span>   
            action <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>b<span class="token operator">></span>Stai<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>b<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token keyword">case</span> <span class="token string">"yellow"</span><span class="token operator">:</span>
            action <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>i<span class="token operator">></span>Finalizeaz캒 manevra<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>i<span class="token operator">></span>
        <span class="token keyword">case</span> <span class="token string">"green"</span><span class="token operator">:</span>
            action <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>strong<span class="token operator">></span>Trece<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>strong<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>  
        <span class="token keyword">default</span><span class="token operator">:</span>
            action <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>span<span class="token operator">></span>Fii atent<span class="token punctuation">,</span> semaforul nu func탵ioneaz캒<span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>span<span class="token operator">></span>  
    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>  
    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>div<span class="token operator">></span>Semaforul recomand캒<span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>action<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>div<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="literali-de-siruri-de-caractere-ca-props-uri" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#literali-de-siruri-de-caractere-ca-props-uri"><span>Literali de 탳iruri de caractere ca props-uri</span></a></h2>
<p>Literali de 탳iruri de caractere pot fi, de asemenea, utiliza탵i ca props-uri.</p>
<p>De exemplu, aceste componente sunt echivalente:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>WelcomeComponent name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"Carol Danvers"</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>WelcomeComponent name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">'Carol Danvers'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>WelcomeComponent name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token template-string"><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span><span class="token string">Carol Danvers</span><span class="token template-punctuation string">`</span></span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>WelcomeComponent name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">'Carol Danvers'</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Dac캒 transmite탵i un literal de 탳ir de caractere 칥ntr-o component캒, toate simbolurile sale posibile vor fi transformate 칥n entit캒탵i HTML corespunz캒toare. Aceste dou캒 componente sunt echivalente:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>FavoritePet pet<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"&amp;#128008;"</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>FavoritePet pet<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token string">'游낻'</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="valorile-implicite-ale-props-urilor-sunt-true" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#valorile-implicite-ale-props-urilor-sunt-true"><span>Valorile implicite ale props-urilor sunt true</span></a></h2>
<p>Dac캒 se transmite o valoare 칥ntr-un prop, implicit va fi <mark>true</mark>.
Aceste dou캒 expresii JSX sunt echivalente:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>TextInput disabled <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>TextInput disabled<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Aceast캒 caracteristic캒 a props-urilor 칥n componentele React exist캒 pentru a se conforma comportamentului HTML obi탳nuit. Este mai bine s캒 nu v캒 baza탵i pe aceast캒 caracteristic캒 탳i s캒 specifica탵i valorile props-urilor 칥n mod explicit, deoarece altfel aceast캒 칥nregistrare poate fi interpretat캒 de React ca o nota탵ie scurt캒 a propriet캒탵ilor obiectului:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> title <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token string">"Autostop prin Moldova"</span>

<span class="token punctuation">{</span> title <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Aceast캒 칥nregistrare este echivalent캒 cu obiectul <mark>{ title: &quot;Autostop prin Moldova&quot; }</mark>, dar cu siguran탵캒 nu cu obiectul <mark>{ title: true }</mark>.</p>
<h2 id="atribute-de-extindere" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#atribute-de-extindere"><span>Atribute de extindere</span></a></h2>
<p>Structura 칥ncorporat캒 a props-urilor este o situa탵ie frecvent캒, mai ales c칙nd lucra탵i cu</p>
<p>un server care returneaz캒 un JSON multi-nivel. Pentru a face codul mai compact 탳i mai lizibil, pute탵i utiliza operatorul de extindere. 칉n acest exemplu, ambele componente sunt identice:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">CutomerPage</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>ProfileInfo 
            firstName<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>profileData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>firstName<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
            lastName<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>profileData<span class="token punctuation">.</span>lastName<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
        <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>

<span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">CutomerPage</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">props</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>ProfileInfo <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token operator">...</span>props<span class="token punctuation">.</span>profileData<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>Operatorul de extindere ajut캒 la filtrarea props-urilor necesare 탳i la transmiterea 칥n componenta 탵int캒 doar a datelor necesare:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Input</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token parameter">props</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> size<span class="token punctuation">,</span> userId<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">...</span>otherProps <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> props<span class="token punctuation">;</span>  
    <span class="token keyword">const</span> className <span class="token operator">=</span> size <span class="token operator">===</span> <span class="token string">"default"</span> <span class="token operator">?</span> <span class="token string">"DefaultInput"</span> <span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"SmallInput"</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
  <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>input className<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>className<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token operator">...</span>otherProps<span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>

<span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">LandingPage</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
  <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>
    <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">></span>
            <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>b<span class="token operator">></span>Introduce탵i codul promo탵ional<span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span>b<span class="token operator">></span>     
            <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>Input size<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"default"</span> type<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">"text"</span> disabled<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> userId<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token number">1112983</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>    
        <span class="token operator">&lt;</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">></span>
    <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n acest exemplu, 칥n componenta <mark>Input</mark> sunt transmise urm캒toarele props-uri:</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js" data-title="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token punctuation">{</span>
    <span class="token literal-property property">size</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token string">"default"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
    <span class="token literal-property property">type</span><span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token string">"text"</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> 
    <span class="token literal-property property">disabled</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> 
    <span class="token literal-property property">userId</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">1112983</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>칉n timp ce props-urile <mark>size</mark> 탳i <mark>userId</mark> sunt folosite 칥n siguran탵캒 탳i nu sunt transmise 칥n elementul DOM <mark>&lt;input/&gt;</mark>. Prop-ul <mark>size</mark> este folosit intern pentru a calcula clasa, iar <mark>userId</mark> nu este folosit deloc.
Prin urmare, 칥n obiectul <mark>otherProps</mark> r캒m칙n doar props-urile necesare elementului DOM - <mark>type</mark> 탳i <mark>disabled</mark>.</p>
<p>Atributele de extindere pot fi utile 탳i reduc codul, dar exist캒 riscul de a transmite props-uri suplimentare 칥n componente sau atribute HTML nevalide 칥n DOM. Utiliza탵i acest instrument cu pruden탵캒.</p>
<h2 id="props-uri-pe-scurt-despre-principal" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#props-uri-pe-scurt-despre-principal"><span>Props-uri: pe scurt despre principal</span></a></h2>
<p>칉n aceast캒 lec탵ie, ne-am aprofundat 칥n posibilit캒탵ile props-urilor componentelor React.</p>
<p>Reamintim cele mai importante aspecte:</p>
<ul>
<li>Props-urile pot fi doar citite.</li>
<li>Props-urile pot fi orice expresii JavaScript.</li>
<li>Implicit, valorile props-urilor sunt setate la true.</li>
<li>Props-urile pot fi transmise 칥n bloc cu ajutorul operatorului de extindere.</li>
<li>Un dezvoltator React aplic캒 aceste abilit캒탵i 칥n mod regulat, iar abilitatea de a &quot;prepara&quot; corect props-urile influen탵eaz캒 semnificativ calitatea 탳i fiabilitatea codului. 칉n lec탵ia urm캒toare, vom discuta despre starea intern캒 탳i vom analiza cum s캒 o utiliz캒m 칥mpreun캒 cu props-urile.</li>
